ps://profiles.wordpress.org/yordansoares"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/940ca4a79fdd1630d25049f2aefb20a5?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/940ca4a79fdd1630d25049f2aefb20a5?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/yordansoares" class="reviewer-name">YordanSoares</a> el <span class="review-date">March 17, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">I use this plugin for almost my projects and I don\'t ever had any  problems with it. Some of the features of this plugin:\n\n- Easy to use.\n- Compatible with any template.\n- Customizable: CSS, HTML and JS.\n\nThe unique disadvantage CF7 was that you couln\'t save messages in database... until now: Takayuki Miyoshi made a extension called Flamingo that stores all your received messages in database. Also take a look to this one plugin ;)</div>\n</div>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n				<h4 class="review-title">Easy use</h4>\n				<div class="star-rating">\n				<div class="wporg-ratings" aria-label="5 de 5 estrellas" data-title-template="%s de 5 estrellas" data-rating="5" style="color:#ffb900;"><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class="reviewer">\n				Por <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/ashmtl"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6169d91f9de89705e4201cc93017a40a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6169d91f9de89705e4201cc93017a40a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/ashmtl" class="reviewer-name">Ashod <small>(ashmtl)</small></a> el <span class="review-date">March 16, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">My review will be partial because I didn\'t have time to explore the possibilities of the form. For now I am using it for a simple contact form and was able to set it up using my intuition. The same goes for reCAPTCHA setup. The form is well documented and intuitive.</div>\n</div>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n				<h4 class="review-title">what a shame</h4>\n				<div class="star-rating">\n				<div class="wporg-ratings" aria-label="1 de 5 estrellas" data-title-template="%s de 5 estrellas" data-rating="1" style="color:#ffb900;"><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class="reviewer">\n				Por <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/getonlinego"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2ffc62c93e952d8cd78d5031174d2f2a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2ffc62c93e952d8cd78d5031174d2f2a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/getonlinego" class="reviewer-name">getonlinego</a> el <span class="review-date">March 15, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">was a good plugin, is \'garbage\' and useless now since you stuffed up the \'reCaptcha\'... DO NOT UPDATE the app to the latest... 5.05 or earlier only!\n\n...I suggest you find another contact app that is supported and updated properly!</div>\n</div>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n				<h4 class="review-title">Excellent</h4>\n				<div class="star-rating">\n				<div class="wporg-ratings" aria-label="5 de 5 estrellas" data-title-template="%s de 5 estrellas" data-rating="5" style="color:#ffb900;"><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class="reviewer">\n				Por <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/massimoroccia"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/af1ef8266de4cbe3139675a6b1d32f12?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/af1ef8266de4cbe3139675a6b1d32f12?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/massimoroccia" class="reviewer-name">Max.R <small>(massimoroccia)</small></a> el <span class="review-date">March 14, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">This plugin is just excellent, it works perfectly, exactly what is needed for a very good WordPress contact form.</div>\n</div>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n				<h4 class="review-title">The issue with reCaptcha killed the plugin</h4>\n				<div class="star-rating">\n				<div class="wporg-ratings" aria-label="1 de 5 estrellas" data-title-template="%s de 5 estrellas" data-rating="1" style="color:#ffb900;"><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class="reviewer">\n				Por <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/pzanto"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ae71e840f593f2f7be98986bc5c66da5?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ae71e840f593f2f7be98986bc5c66da5?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/pzanto" class="reviewer-name">pzanto</a> el <span class="review-date">March 14, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">What used to be a simple and reliable plugin now its not being able to use anymore in my sites because of the issue with reCaptcha. Sad, i hope gets fixed soon</div>\n</div>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n				<h4 class="review-title">Do not use this plugin</h4>\n				<div class="star-rating">\n				<div class="wporg-ratings" aria-label="1 de 5 estrellas" data-title-template="%s de 5 estrellas" data-rating="1" style="color:#ffb900;"><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class="reviewer">\n				Por <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/cirymarr"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/574931d9449699a7f27a38020cd23e2d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/574931d9449699a7f27a38020cd23e2d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/cirymarr" class="reviewer-name">cirymarr</a> el <span class="review-date">March 12, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">Sometimes, we all purchase plugins on the assumption that it will work, and that an acceptable level of support will be provided by the author/developer of said plugin.\n\nContact Form 7 WAS a good plugin for Contact Form creation, until recently, when the developer decided to remove support for reCaptcha V2 and ONLY provide support for reCaptcha V3.  reCaptcha v3, when implemented, results in lots and lots of spam (i.e. it doesn\'t work).  \n\nOnly older versions of Contact Form 7 support reCaptcha V2.  Many customers have posted this issue, but the developer appears to have his head buried in the sand.\n\nMy advice - use another quality Contact Form plugin. I have.</div>\n</div>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n				<h4 class="review-title">set up is obtusely difficult</h4>\n				<div class="star-rating">\n				<div class="wporg-ratings" aria-label="1 de 5 estrellas" data-title-template="%s de 5 estrellas" data-rating="1" style="color:#ffb900;"><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class="reviewer">\n				Por <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/flyfisher842"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ee2dbdd6d7aed753dbae1691569fd0a0?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ee2dbdd6d7aed753dbae1691569fd0a0?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/flyfisher842" class="reviewer-name">flyfisher842</a> el <span class="review-date">March 7, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">When you have invalid mail syntax, the explanation of how to resolve these errors is obtuse and difficult to understand.  Basically you might as well google for the answer.\n\nwhat used to be simple is not simple any longer</div>\n</div>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n				<h4 class="review-title">From leader to lost plugin</h4>\n				<div class="star-rating">\n				<div class="wporg-ratings" aria-label="1 de 5 estrellas" data-title-template="%s de 5 estrellas" data-rating="1" style="color:#ffb900;"><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class="reviewer">\n				Por <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/jeshl"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a73733ef82f0dd5dc690ce81019c3568?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a73733ef82f0dd5dc690ce81019c3568?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/jeshl" class="reviewer-name">jeshl</a> el <span class="review-date">March 4, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">I imagine at some point you just feel like enough is enough and you stop supporting the plugin right? Made enough money, had enough fun. Been an institution in WPO for a decade. And now they have walked away. Came here looking for fixes to a wpcf7.initForm issue, which was supposedly addressed, but I am still having it. And I read THOUSANDS of other people walking away from cf7. don\'t install this plugin apparently. They went on vacation and aren\'t expected back</div>\n</div>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n				<h4 class="review-title">Contact form7 with a reCaptcha v3 does not work reliable</h4>\n				<div class="star-rating">\n				<div class="wporg-ratings" aria-label="1 de 5 estrellas" data-title-template="%s de 5 estrellas" data-rating="1" style="color:#ffb900;"><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class="reviewer">\n				Por <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/xnosek00"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bccf77c6a02f2a343834d3f6bca2d2cd?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bccf77c6a02f2a343834d3f6bca2d2cd?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/xnosek00" class="reviewer-name">xnosek00</a> el <span class="review-date">March 3, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">Plugin is not reliable because of changing reCaptcha v2 to reCaptcha v3. \nReCaptcha v3 isn\'t reliable. There is not possible to submit form, because reCAPTCHA v3 says: error: reCAPTCHA v3 test failed. \n\nSometimes it is possible to sent form, but often it isn\'t possible. After testing it, 10 forms were submitted and 20 forms not. Now I\'m trying to sumbit form, but it is not possible. \n\nI can\'t risk, that clients can\'t write me. Moving to reCaptcha v3 should be optionable but not obligatory. Plugin is now unusable. Who wants website, which sometimes works and sometimes not? \n\nIf your website does not work, you see problem. You can solve it. But when you are using this plugin, you doesn\'t see problem. Website looks like pretty. But when are you cli